%N A394816 Numbers k such that sigma(k) = psi(k) + tau(k) + Omega(k)^5.
%e A394816 3796 is a term since sigma(3796) = 7252 = 6216 + 12 + 4^5 = psi(3796) + tau(3796) + Omega(3796)^5.
%o A394816 (PARI) isok(k) = {my(f = factor(k)); sigma(f) == prod(i=1, #f~, (f[i, 1]+1) * f[i, 1]^(f[i, 2]-1)) + numdiv(f) + bigomega(f)^5; } \\ _Amiram Eldar_, Apr 02 2026
